enum FdoRasterDataType
 

The FdoRasterDataType enumeration specifies the type of data stored in the Raster Image.

Parameters:
FdoRasterDataType_Unknown Data is organized in an unknown or provider specific manner.
FdoRasterDataType_UnsignedInteger Data is organized as Unsigned Integers.
FdoRasterDataType_Integer Data is organized as Signed Integers.
FdoRasterDataType_Float Data is organized as Floats.
FdoRasterDataType_Double Data is organized as Doubles.
